{"tid":413882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【城巴奪命】的士城巴真係有鬥車？ 的士乘客還原事發前","createTime":"2017-09-25T17:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T09:36:48.000Z","uid":11095,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87bec1c3c6216f271f2cd084760bc5c924d19951","tid":413882,"uid":11095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T17:57:25.000Z","msg":"深水埗城巴大車禍慘劇發生超過一日(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yiS42D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yiS42D&d=xKweJY0nUZaYDGenUJ7eAE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c3d8498e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yiS42D</a>)，警方繼續調查車禍原因，至昨晚警方發出呼籲，當時停在肇事城巴前方的一部的士內，可能目擊意外經過的男乘客致電3661 9058與警方聯絡及提供消息。《蘋果》找到該名男乘客李先生，他表示已聯絡警方，稍後會到警署提供相關資料，更直言：「我會盡番一個巿民嘅責任，希望還的士司機一個清白！」<br />\n<br />\n家住太子道西的李先生憶述，事發前與爸爸在荔枝角道登上該部的士，正準備返回寓所，沿途一切如常，司機亦無出現加速或突然減速的情況。直至駛至現場，的士慢慢收慢停低，李先生曾抬頭見燈號由黃燈轉紅燈，沒料到，突然車尾被撞一撞，「chok一chok，衝力唔太大，我仲以為係私家車撞上嚟，點知見到架巴士已經喺左邊，衝上行人路！」意外來得突然，他直言當時「我哋3個人(其父及司機)都呆晒」。<br />\n李先生與爸爸立即落車睇，見到車頭有女途人被壓著半身，「好恐怖，有乘客流血，廣告架卡住車頂。」他形容當時情況相當混亂，其後警察到場，有太多事情要處理，遂着他們父子先行離去。直至昨晚得知警方欲聯絡他們，遂立即與警方聯絡。對於外界一直有人質疑，車禍與的士司機有關，更指摘的士司機與城巴司機鬥車才釀成車禍，惟李先生卻相當肯定的說「冇咁嘅事」，並一句就為的士司機解脫：「(過程中)根本完全冇見過呢架城巴出現！」他認為的士司機駕駛態度無問題，見他心情亦輕鬆，「司機好友善，上車時仲傾咗陣計」，其間並沒有出現脾氣暴躁的情況，他記憶中的士有車cam，相信可以找到真相。<br />\n不過，畢竟發生如此多人死傷的大車禍，李先生坦言，如果當時巴士直撞的士，後果亦不堪設想，自言：「真係好好彩，但發生咁大車禍，心情亦相當難過，希望傷者可以早日康復。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170924/57248027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170924%2F57248027&d=xKweJY0nUZaYDGenUJ7eAE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f75f14f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170924%2F57248027&h=fa4d961b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170924/57248027</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170924/large/1506184996_e3ee.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170924%2Flarge%2F1506184996_e3ee.jpg&d=xKweJY0nUZaYDGenUJ7eAE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=87992b12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170924%2Flarge%2F1506184996_e3ee.jpg&h=698a6fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170924/large/1506184996_e3ee.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n撐的士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得巴士司機值得同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ec48e96cab95a4fdf4cef6f9330d6b00ca8779","tid":413882,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:14:56.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"8fe11b43352b2e5333aaa2493e9a57c22d364e0b","tid":413882,"uid":8129,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:24:11.000Z","msg":"連燈籽又炒車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6becf5528451a26bee4ea4b7393a4d820ec0b70","tid":413882,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:38:39.000Z","msg":"的士有車 cam ，旁邊大把車有車 cam ，唔使驚"},{"pid":"b19f12fa58d2272746f403e4427078d555d81625","tid":413882,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁真係城巴佬恰眼訓"},{"pid":"2ccaa5d14574dd1438f1785fa3735b45440da016","tid":413882,"uid":4213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁真係城巴佬恰眼訓</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死巴膠含撚啦<br />\n見到你班毒撚都眼冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"49bdf5daff5fb7b4b29e71a7225045980e35b688","tid":413882,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy